      <div class="divider"></div>
      <p class="about-text">Bucket Dynamics is a high school engineering project built around one idea: drones shouldn't be locked into a single purpose. Every part of our platform (sensors, payload, power) is designed to snap in and out so you can change the setup without starting over.</p>
      <p class="about-text" style="margin-top: -0.5rem;">The frame is 3D printed using carbon fiber filament, keeping it light without sacrificing strength. We designed and built everything from scratch.</p>

      <div class="about-pillars">
        <div class="pillar">
          <div class="pillar-icon">01</div>
          <h4>Carbon Fiber Frame</h4>
          <p>3D printed with carbon fiber filament, strong, lightweight, and fully custom designed by our team.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pillar">
